HER MAJESTY QUEEN RAMBHAI BARNI OF SIAM BEING INTRODUCED TO GUESTS ON ARRIVAL IN SINGAPORE

Description Edited by NAS:

Queen Rambhai Barni being received by well-wishers upon arrival in Singapore. The Queen was escorting the royal ashes of her husband, King Prajadhipok, back to Thailand from United Kingdom.

Covering Date:

18/05/1949
